      • copyTo

        public void copyTo(DigitalObject dobj)
            throws RepositoryException,
                   java.io.IOException
        Description copied from interface: SupportsFastCopyForLayeredRepo
        Copy this digital object (in the bottom repository of a LayeredRepository to another digital object (in the top repository). For implementations that can be faster than naive copying. In general this does not copy the data of data elements, but sets the attribute LayeredDataElement.ATTRIBUTE_DATA_ELEMENT_MISSING to 1 on each data element not copied.
        Specified by:
        copyTo in interface SupportsFastCopyForLayeredRepo
        Parameters:
